  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Adefuwa &amp; Elijah – Wedding Invitation</title>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       LINK PREVIEW (WhatsApp, iMessage, Twitter)

       ✅  HOW TO SET THE PREVIEW IMAGE (do this once):
       1. Go to cloudinary.com → your Media Library
       2. Upload your hero/couple photo
       3. Click the image → copy the URL
       4. Add these transforms to the URL for WhatsApp:
          Change /upload/ to /upload/w_1200,h_630,c_fill,q_auto,f_jpg/
       5. Paste that URL into og:image AND twitter:image below
       6. Update og:url to your live Netlify URL

       ⚠️  WHY WHATSAPP FAILS WITH NETLIFY:
       - WhatsApp crawls og:image independently of your site
       - If the image isn't live yet, or >300KB, or on a slow host → no preview
       - Cloudinary is always-on and fast → guaranteed to work
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
