      <p class="rsvp-modal-eyebrow">Wedding RSVP</p>
      <p class="rsvp-modal-names">Adefuwa <em>&amp;</em> Elijah</p>
      <p class="rsvp-modal-date">August 6th &amp; 8th, 2026 · Ibadan, Oyo State</p>
